DevOps stages

Plan 
Code
    Git
Build
    Maven
    Gradle

Testing
    Junit
    Selenium

Integration - once testing is done, the new features are integrated automatically to the existing codebase
    Jenkins
    
Deployment
    Application is packaged after release and deployed from dev server to prod server 
    XebiaLabs
    bmc

Operate - once software is deployed,  the ops teams perform activities such as configuring servers and provisioning them with the required resources
    Ansible
    Chef 
    
Monitoring
    Nagios
    Splunk
    OSSEC

